In my purse.

36:02.627 --> 36:04.652
Thank God!
Which is in the car.

36:08.600 --> 36:10.795
Hey, that's my gun!
What?

36:10.869 --> 36:13.633
Oh, yeah. No, I borrowed it.
And be glad I did.

36:20.812 --> 36:22.677
Will somebody please
tell me what's going on?

36:22.747 --> 36:25.648
Reese and Lindsey Bishop
were having an affair.

36:25.717 --> 36:27.844
They were
the fornicators!

36:28.620 --> 36:30.110
Things must
have gone bad.

36:30.188 --> 36:32.418
Maybe she threatened
to tell his wife.

36:32.490 --> 36:33.889
All we know
for sure...

36:33.958 --> 36:35.016
Oh, God!

36:35.093 --> 36:36.754
He wanted her gone.

36:36.828 --> 36:38.853
It was a setup
from the beginning.

36:38.930 --> 36:40.727
He was going to
kill his mistress

36:40.799 --> 36:43.495
and make it look like an
inmate did it during an escape.

36:43.568 --> 36:46.036
JACK, JR: Yeah, he went to Shiv.
It was the perfect choice.

36:46.104 --> 36:47.366
The guy's a real moron.

36:47.439 --> 36:49.999
It worked,
Shiv took the bait.

36:52.610 --> 36:54.237
Reese told Shiv

36:54.312 --> 36:56.075
how to go,
where to go,

36:56.147 --> 36:58.877
and most importantly,
when to go.

36:58.950 --> 37:01.680
It had to be Monday night at 3:00.

37:07.759 --> 37:11.593
That night,
he killed Lindsey Bishop in the parking lot,

37:12.063 --> 37:14.361
then he reported for duty,

37:14.432 --> 37:17.731
took his position in the
guard tower and waited.

37:23.875 --> 37:27.504
He expected Shiv to be
climbing out any minute.

37:28.947 --> 37:31.780
He didn't know that Jack Monk,
Jr. Had other ideas.

37:32.350 --> 37:34.477
It wasn't exactly how
Reese planned it.

37:34.552 --> 37:37.146
But he didn't care.
One patsy's as good as another.

37:53.204 --> 37:56.401
I'm out! Oh, God.
Oh, God, oh, God!

38:00.712 --> 38:03.010
He stopped. He stopped.
Did you get him?

38:03.081 --> 38:04.571
Well, I don't know.

38:04.649 --> 38:05.673
Hold on.

38:05.750 --> 38:06.978
No, Mr. Monk,
what are you doing?

38:09.621 --> 38:11.384
Quick, go, go!
Come on!

38:14.159 --> 38:16.024
Come on! We have
to get to my purse!

38:17.829 --> 38:19.820
I'll go.
I'll go.

38:19.898 --> 38:22.731
No, I'll go! You stay!
I want to do it!

38:22.801 --> 38:24.200
Are you sure?

38:27.839 --> 38:29.636
You were wrong
about me, brother!

38:30.775 --> 38:32.538
Throw me the keys!
Keys.

38:32.610 --> 38:34.202
Oh, God,
oh, God!

38:35.513 --> 38:37.174
Sorry.

38:49.127 --> 38:50.458
He made it!

38:53.298 --> 38:55.766
He's backing up.
Mr. Monk, he's backing up.

38:56.334 --> 38:57.665
Wait!

38:58.937 --> 39:00.461
