39:00.538 --> 39:03.871
Paraguay.
The most beautiful women in the world.

39:04.242 --> 39:06.904
No. Mr. Monk.
Here he comes.

39:07.946 --> 39:09.106
Oh, no, what do we do?

39:09.180 --> 39:11.011
Okay. Okay.

39:12.016 --> 39:13.415
I'm going to count to three.

39:13.485 --> 39:15.316
Okay. Yes, okay.

39:15.386 --> 39:16.648
On three,

39:17.555 --> 39:19.352
you come up
with a great idea.

39:41.579 --> 39:44.070
Paraguay
is that way.

39:44.782 --> 39:46.147
The beautiful women.

39:52.874 --> 39:54.398
Good deal, thank you.

39:54.976 --> 39:58.309
That was the DA.
He says that Reese is awake

39:58.379 --> 40:02.008
and pouring his heart out.
We got him on Lindsey Bishop and Shiv Logan.

40:02.517 --> 40:03.745
What about Jack?

40:04.218 --> 40:07.381
Well, he did escape, so they're gonna
add a little time to his sentence.

40:09.357 --> 40:10.824
He wanted to
say goodbye.

40:11.592 --> 40:13.059
Figured he was
family, right?

40:13.127 --> 40:14.560
Yeah. He's...

40:14.962 --> 40:16.293
He's family.

40:16.664 --> 40:18.859
It's almost worth it,
hearing you say that.

40:18.933 --> 40:21.527
Hey, uh, Bayside
Correctional is only

40:21.602 --> 40:24.469
