Maybe you could come up sometime.

40:24.539 --> 40:27.133
Yeah, I could do that.
Maybe one day.

40:30.311 --> 40:32.074
All right, Jack,
time to go.

40:33.848 --> 40:34.906
See you.

40:34.982 --> 40:36.142
Jack.

40:36.551 --> 40:40.317
Listen, I just wanted to say
I'm proud of what you did.

40:41.356 --> 40:44.348
And I'm proud
you're my brother.

40:45.226 --> 40:46.989
You mean half-brother.

40:48.029 --> 40:49.621
I'm rounding up.

40:55.737 --> 40:59.298
Excuse me.
I'm just going to sneak in here. Sorry.

41:10.385 --> 41:11.613
Thank you.

41:21.662 --> 41:22.788
Jack.

